		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>A Brave New World</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP">
			<Text>Just as it has always been, when our memories of the ancient world fade into twilight - a new era dawns to fill the void... [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]With this comes the responsibility of knowing the decisions you make today will have a lasting impact in the generations of tomorrow.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Receive a Great Person of your choice.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>A village then grows to a nation. An empire. A free unit appears near every City.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>A unique experience enjoyed by the many. +1 [ICON_HAPPINESS_1] Happiness per City!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Dark times plagued by the corruption of man has caused strife in our nation. Every City revolts amongst the chaos and 2 Barbarian appears near every City.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Gain a free Policy in the name of social progress!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_HELP_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>A long heroic Golden Age numbering {4_Turns} begins for our Empire.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Through our vision, unique perspectives enter the world and unlock the secrets of the universe.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Advancement in military theory brought devastation to the world like none have ever seen.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Creating new designs that brought the world stage onto the masses and providing an experience, that many could ever imagine.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Consumed by war and conflict, we have found little solace, rushing to actions on impulse, without forethought.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>However, there still exist of men who spread their ideologies with a heavy hand. And yet, some chose a different path striving for peace in their endeavors.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_CIV_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>Although mankind will always look onward, yearning for more, searching for new boundaries, only to break through them with the understanding that this world is one which we all live in and share with.</Text>
		</Row>
